data.description: ''Seller to credit up to $10,000 towards buyers closing costs as closing with an acceptable offer made before december 31st. You can enjoy your Cheeseburger in Paradise, sipping on a Boat Drink in Latitude Margaritaville! This popular Cabana floor plan boasts a true 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms, an office, and many upgrades, including but not limited to a whole home water filtration system, plantation shutters throughout the home, custom closet in the master bedroom and custom kitchen pantry, saltwater pool with a Hayward electric heat pump; installed 2022. Professionally installed exterior lighting at the front of the home and pool area, and the original lanai was converted to a sunroom! Latitude Margaritaville offers the finest amenities, fitness and wellness center, pool, and golf cart friendly Publix shopping center right across the way!  Also enjoy the private restaurant and the Private Beach Club!"
